\
a) Withhold sex further \'96 he\'92s not going to win this game!\
\
b) Cry and whine and demand answers he\'92s not yet ready to give, further alienating him.\
\
c) Have faith that this is just a bump in a long marriage \'96 he is in a dark place \'96 so try to be understanding and wait it out.\
